<div class="inner" id="msg_1067824"><span style="color: brown;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-size: 16pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>Roll20 忍神跑团教学</strong></span></span><br><hr />　　Roll20为西方主流的跑团平台，大多被认为适合战棋系或开放世界规则。但若套用忍神角色模板，roll20也可以带来高品质的忍神体验。本文将总结笔者使用roll20跑团后的心得与注意事项。<br><br>　　网址：<a href="https://app.roll20.net/" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">https://app.roll20.net/</a><br>　　注：需翻墙使用，无VPN可浏览网站，但可能无法载入房间。电脑VPN也进不去的话，浏览器可换成Chrome试试。<span style="color: maroon;" class="bbc_color">本平台适用电脑，手机体验差。</span><br><hr /><span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>目录：</strong></span></span><br><br><span style="font-family: 楷体;" class="bbc_font">一、帐号／房间与建议设定<br></span><ul class="bbc_list" style="list-style-type: decimal;"><li><span style="font-family: 楷体;" class="bbc_font">帐号语系设定</span><li><span style="font-family: 楷体;" class="bbc_font">忍神房间设定</span><li><span style="font-family: 楷体;" class="bbc_font">建立房间</span><li><span style="font-family: 楷体;" class="bbc_font">邀请玩家</span><li><span style="font-family: 楷体;" class="bbc_font">其他建议设定</span></ul><br><span style="font-family: 楷体;" class="bbc_font">二、角色卡设置／数据录入<br><br>三、相关功能<br></span><ul class="bbc_list" style="list-style-type: decimal;"><li><span style="font-family: 楷体;" class="bbc_font">使用角色头像对话</span><li><span style="font-family: 楷体;" class="bbc_font">token建立</span><li><span style="font-family: 楷体;" class="bbc_font">token血量设定</span><li><span style="font-family: 楷体;" class="bbc_font">一键投表</span><li><span style="font-family: 楷体;" class="bbc_font">自动特技判定</span><li><span style="font-family: 楷体;" class="bbc_font">自动忍法判定</span><li><span style="font-family: 楷体;" class="bbc_font">忍法配图</span><li><span style="font-family: 楷体;" class="bbc_font">谋位与GM私讯</span><li><span style="font-family: 楷体;" class="bbc_font">注意事项</span></ul><br><span style="font-family: 楷体;" class="bbc_font">四、GM相关<br></span><ul class="bbc_list" style="list-style-type: decimal;"><li><span style="font-family: 楷体;" class="bbc_font">图层</span><li><span style="font-family: 楷体;" class="bbc_font">场景切换</span><li><span style="font-family: 楷体;" class="bbc_font">BGM设定</span></ul><br><span style="font-family: 楷体;" class="bbc_font">五、LOG导出与整理</span></div>
</div>
