<div class="inner" id="msg_1067829"><span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>四、GM相关</strong></span></span><br><hr /><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;"><strong>1. 图层：</strong><br>roll20图层分为地图(最底)、token(地图之上，以格为单位)、gm(玩家不可视)三类。Gm可借由图层配置战场表、CG等<br><img src="https://i.imgur.com/7MFrK7d.png" alt="" class="bbc_img"/><br><br><strong>2. 场景切换：</strong><br>右上页面图标，可以编辑地图场景。<br><img src="https://i.imgur.com/Qi2lAk1.png" alt="" class="bbc_img"/><br><br>．借由预先设置多个场景，可达到顺畅的转场效果（每个场景亦可设定不同BGM）<br><img src="https://i.imgur.com/3gWWVIH.png" alt="" class="bbc_img"/><br><br>．拖曳红色书签，可将玩家跳转至指定场景页面<br><img src="https://i.imgur.com/GtyOOFZ.png" alt="" class="bbc_img"/><br><br><br><br><strong>3. BGM：</strong><br>roll20汇入bgm十分容易。在首页的工具中有音乐库可上传，并在游戏中的点唱机可自由拨放。<br><img src="https://i.imgur.com/AlBmNwO.png" alt="" class="bbc_img"/><br></div></div></div></div>
